attributes.Long form description: The student's task is to disassemble the IKEA KNAVERRIK table, so he starts by attempting to unscrew the hex socket head from the legs, however, the student flips the furniture over, and by instruction of the instructor, he must unscrew it with the furniture on stand. Once he corrects his mistake, he starts to slightly unscrew the hex socket head of each leg with an Allen wrench, after unscrewing, he starts by removing each hex socket head from the top table, then he disassembles the top table from the legs. Next, the student will disassemble the legs from the shelf by removing each screw from the legs and removing the legs from the shelf. Finally, he finishes by disassembling the last leg of the shelf to place them both on the table.

attributes.Transcription: Now we're going to disassemble this furniture.
